description:
This is a 10 minute workout called 'Mindfulness Meditation - Guided 10 Minutes' from the channel The Honest Guys - Meditations - Relaxation.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Sleep Prep vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Mindfulness has been shown to be very beneficial. (details below) Join our community/see our products: https://www.thehonestguys.co.uk/products

In this guided mindfulness meditation you can learn to be completely present in the moment, letting go of your thoughts and achieving calmness.

This MP3 audio available here:  https://www.thehonestguys.co.uk/digital-downloads/mindfulness-meditation-guided-10-minutes

THE HONEST GUYS
We create effortless ways for anyone to reach a profound sense of deep relaxation, meditation and sleep, without ever having to try. We offer this through high-quality audio productions, called 'guided visualisations'. These include sleep talk-downs, meditations, wonderful fantasy imagery and stories.
